			<a href="http://imgs.xkcd.com/comics/tech_support_cheat_sheet.png">Best</a>
		</div>
		
		<div>
			<h2>Favorite Quotes</h2>
			
			<!-- <p> tags indicate a text paragraph -->
			<p>
				<!-- html has a variety of tags for formating text. They include <b> for bold, <i> for italics, and <br> for line break. -->
				<b>Terry Pratchett</b> - <br> <i>Always be wary of any helpful item that weighs less than its operating manual.</i> 
